name: Tiamonds
description: Tiamonds is transforming how we think about owning and trading real-world assets. Initially focused on tokenizing diamonds, Tiamonds 2.0 takes it a step further, expanding to include a wide range of assets such as commodities, real estate, art, collectibles, and financial instruments. With the power of blockchain, Tiamonds makes it easy to own and trade assets securely, without the traditional barriers like storage or shipping costs.
